Cell["\<\
The loading of precompiled binaries is controlled by \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]wbLoadBinaries\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]. If \
wbLoadBinaries == True, the binaries are loaded. If wbLoadBinaries == False, \
or if wbLoadBinaries is not specified, the functions are compiled locally.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.978608817044029*^9, 3.978608821835504*^9}, {
  3.978784054529261*^9, 3.978784076555791*^9}, {3.982126885672341*^9, 
