Cell[TextData[{
 "1. Most of command names are in singular form (i.e. ",
 ButtonBox["wbWeinParRndUni",
  BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
  ButtonData->{
    FrontEnd`FileName[{"Documentation"}, "wbWeinParRnd.nb", CharacterEncoding -> 
     "UTF-8"], None}],
 ").  \n2. Options, messages are defined along with the definitions of \
command. \n3. For option names we use Strings. Exceptions are options that \
are present in Mathematica system."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.978437461171164*^9, 3.978437465322587*^9}, {
   3.9787859449310827`*^9, 3.97878594555975*^9}, {3.978786041346834*^9, 
