Cell["\<\
A function that filters the couplings according to additional necessary BFB \
conditions (NCL2 - NCL3).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.979295163611305*^9, 3.9792952824255533`*^9}, {
  3.9792955056261473`*^9, 3.979295546922833*^9}, {3.980930245281704*^9, 
